import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import {
  faCheck,
  faTimes,
  faCheckCircle,
  faTimesCircle,
  faTrashAlt,
  faBars,
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
import { faFacebookF, faGoogle } from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons'

library.add(
  faCheck,
  faTimes,
  faCheckCircle,
  faTimesCircle,
  faTrashAlt,
  faBars,
  faFacebookF,
  faGoogle
)
